OL,3,CHome Office appears to backtrack plans
OL,4,Cto hike family visa threshold to
OL,5,C#38,000
OL,7,FThe Home Office appears to have made a
OL,8,FU-turn on its decision to hike the
OL,9,Fearnings threshold for a family visa
OL,10,Fto #38,700, and will instead increase
OL,11,Fit to #29,000 in the spring.
OL,13,FThe new level is still a substantial
OL,14,Fincrease on the current threshold of
OL,15,F#18,600, and appeared to be confirmed
OL,16,Fin the answer to a parliamentary
OL,17,Fquestion.
OL,19,FThe visa allows British citizens to
OL,20,Fbring foreign family members to the UK
OL,21,Fif they earn enough money.
